==Talisman==
Depending on the player's map coordinates at the moment they kill a monster or open a [[mystery box]], it can drop either a [[chaos talisman]] or [[nature talisman]]. Overworld monsters drop the [[nature talisman]], whereas underground monsters drop the [[chaos talisman]] if they are found within the region shown below. [[Fire giant]]s, for example, might drop a chaos talisman inside the [[Waterfall Dungeon]] but a nature talisman inside the [[Giants' Den]].

